---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — santoshchandu.com" description="About this blog and its author.">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="content-container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <div class="section-label">About</div>
        <h1>About this blog</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content">
        <p>
          This is a personal blog about things I find genuinely interesting in AI and software development.
          Not takes for engagement. Not sponsored content. Just notes from someone paying attention.
        </p>

        <p>
          I write when something strikes me as actually important — a model release that changes how I work,
          a tool that meaningfully improves a workflow, a shift in the landscape that people are under-reacting to.
          The pace is irregular. The quality is the goal.
        </p>

        <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
        <p>
          Posts fall into two main areas: AI developments (new models, research worth reading, practical usage patterns)
          and developer tooling (runtimes, frameworks, protocols, build tools). Occasionally both at once.
        </p>

        <h2>Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          This blog has no analytics, no tracking pixels, no cookies, no ads, no affiliate links.
          I don't know who reads this. That's intentional. Your attention is yours.
        </p>
        <p>
          The RSS feed at <a href="/feed.xml">blog.santoshchandu.com/feed.xml</a> lets you subscribe
          without giving anyone your email address. It's the best way to follow along.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          You can reach me at <a href="mailto:hello@santoshchandu.com">hello@santoshchandu.com</a>.
          I read every email and try to reply to most of them, though it may take a while.
        </p>

        <div class="colophon">
          <p>
            This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, hosted on
            <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com">Cloudflare Pages</a>.
            Source code available on request.
            Type set in Playfair Display and Source Serif 4.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.about-page {
  padding: 3.5rem 0 6rem;
}

.section-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.page-header {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
}

.page-header h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}

.about-content {
  max-width: 62ch;
}

.about-content p {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.about-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.about-content a {
  color: var(--accent);
}

.colophon {
  margin-top: 3.5rem;
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.colophon p {
  font-size: 0.82rem !important;
  color: var(--ink-faint) !important;
  font-style: italic;
}
</style>
